                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-567437751" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-567437751" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="567437751">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/panluan/">潘乱</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一个女人为了一句话搭上一辈子。光字数上就跟《一句顶一万句》有差距，跟《我叫刘跃进》倒更像是姊妹篇，依然是文字大师讲的好故事。学到个新词，入港，不要因小失大。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="595704171">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-595704171" class="vote-count">8</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-595704171" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="595704171">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ashinstancy/">小葵儿</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">欣赏刘震云敢于针砭时弊的勇气，但觉得语言冗余得可怕！（比我可啰嗦多了）</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="643009947">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-643009947" class="vote-count">13</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-643009947" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="643009947">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/summer1018/">大树</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-02-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">刘震云的又一部作品，目测应该有15多万字的序，正文不过1万，而且，题目叫＂玩儿呗＂，可见刘的老练，花五分之四的篇幅，最后是在铺垫一个短篇笑话，一个上访的软文。节奏紧凑题材应景，好几幕让人拍案叫绝。不足有二，题目有点俗艳引人眼球。二，有＜一句顶一万句＞的巅峰作品在先，内容难免略显单薄</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

